aVand with these hydrogenotrophs, you can create a virtuous carbon cycle
p24
aVthat would sustain life onboard a spacecraft.
p25
aVAstronauts would breathe out carbon dioxide,
p26
aVthat carbon dioxide would then be captured by the microbes
p27
aVand converted into a nutritious, carbon-rich crop.
p28
aVThe astronauts would then eat that carbon-rich crop
p29
aVand exhale the carbon out in the form of carbon dioxide,
p30
aVwhich would then be captured by the microbes,
p31
aVto create a nutritious crop,
p32
aVwhich then would be exhaled in the form of carbon dioxide
p33
aVby the astronauts.
