aVAnd this was actually done in the '60s and '70s.
p47
aVSo a colleague of mine, Dr. John Reed, and I,
p48
aVwere interested, actually, in carbon recycling here on Earth.
p49
aVWe wanted to come up with technical solutions
p50
aVto address climate change.
p51
aVAnd we discovered this research
p52
aVby reading some papers published in the '60s \u2014 1967 and later \u2014
p53
aVarticles about this work.
